title: The Walking Dead 400 Days DLC PC [YahSoft]
description:
==========================================================================
             The Walking Dead 400 Days DLC PC[YahSoft]
==========================================================================

This DLC shows the history of the introduction of 5 new characters that will make a second season. is exciting, heavy and little time to think. The typical The Walking Dead.

Minimum System Requirements for The Walking Dead: 400 Days

OS: Windows XP/Vista/7
Processor: Intel Pentium 4 @ 2.0 GHz / AMD Athlon XP 2200+
Memory: 1.5 Gb
Hard Drive: 2 Gb free
Video Memory: 256 Mb
Video Card: nVidia GeForce 8600 / ATI Radeon HD 2600
Sound Card: DirectX Compatible
DirectX: 9.0c

Developer(s)	Telltale Games
Release date(s)	Q4 2013[1]
Genre(s)	Graphic adventure, role-playing

HOW TO INSTALL:

WARNING: It is necessary to have the other 5 episodes before to play this!

1. Download this DLC
2. Open the downloaded folder "The Walking Dead 400 Days DLC PC [YahSoft]", open, and copy ALL the files into the folder where it already installed (provalvelmente should be in c :/ program files / the walking dead
3. If you ask to overwrite existing files press "yes"
4. Play
5. Seed :)
